WEBVTT

01:47.720 --> 01:48.560
Have you made up your mind?

01:49.560 --> 01:51.240
Once I catch Xiaowei,

01:52.160 --> 01:53.880
I'll be able to get into the Shilin Sect.

01:55.200 --> 01:56.080
Then,

01:57.920 --> 01:59.160
I'll kill the Dragon Deity.

02:05.400 --> 02:08.880
One of you here

02:10.039 --> 02:12.320
is the heart-ripping killer I'm after.

02:34.200 --> 02:35.200
It was him!

02:35.720 --> 02:36.920
It was him!

02:37.000 --> 02:38.840
Wu was the one who tied me up!

03:09.800 --> 03:10.680
He's been poisoned.

03:11.680 --> 03:12.560
How could that be?

03:14.160 --> 03:16.320
Shengwei, don't worry.

03:16.920 --> 03:19.360
A powerful demon hunter
from the Shilin Sect is right here.

03:20.360 --> 03:21.560
He'll be fine.

03:23.560 --> 03:25.880
Someone must have poisoned him.

03:26.880 --> 03:29.360
My brother-in-law has never had enemies.

03:30.000 --> 03:31.000
Who would do this?

03:32.760 --> 03:34.680
It seems to be a slow-acting poison.

03:34.760 --> 03:37.320
It'd have to be given
in small doses over time.

03:37.920 --> 03:40.400
Only someone close to him
could've done it.

03:41.600 --> 03:43.280
If we'd found him any later,

03:43.360 --> 03:45.200
he would've been beyond saving.

03:47.640 --> 03:48.680
But even now,

03:48.760 --> 03:51.240
he's in bad shape.

03:51.960 --> 03:56.040
Normally, I could use magic
to draw the poison out of his body.

03:56.560 --> 04:00.080
But my ring's sacred power
is down to a tenth.

04:01.160 --> 04:02.000
I can't save him.

04:03.240 --> 04:05.400
Master Ji Ling, not even you can save him?

04:09.320 --> 04:10.360
Wei Qing.

04:11.440 --> 04:13.400
Wei Qing. Wei Qing…

04:15.440 --> 04:16.680
How did this happen?

04:25.640 --> 04:28.440
If we find the antidote soon enough,
there may still be hope.

04:31.760 --> 04:33.360
-I have--
-Let's go.

04:35.040 --> 04:36.400
-I… I really have--
-Come, let's go.

04:58.920 --> 05:00.440
Thank you, Mr. Ji.

05:01.640 --> 05:02.560
No need.

05:03.160 --> 05:04.560
There's another injured person here.

05:06.640 --> 05:10.120
Miss Yu, your neck wound
looks pretty deep.

05:11.000 --> 05:12.600
If it's not treated properly,

05:13.240 --> 05:14.120
it'll scar.

05:15.520 --> 05:16.880
But…

05:17.840 --> 05:19.360
Mr. Ji, you just said

05:19.440 --> 05:21.880
your sacred power is down to only a tenth.

05:21.960 --> 05:23.960
Can you still heal me?

05:25.440 --> 05:27.160
There's another way.

05:28.280 --> 05:29.120
Here.

05:29.200 --> 05:31.160
A special wound powder
from the Shilin Sect.

05:32.720 --> 05:33.640
It works even better.

05:34.600 --> 05:35.800
Take it.

05:40.920 --> 05:42.480
You… You don't want it?

05:45.960 --> 05:48.360
Mr. Ji, would you be so kind

05:48.960 --> 05:50.080
as to apply it for me?

05:51.640 --> 05:53.120
I'm not familiar with this.

05:54.440 --> 05:55.680
I'm afraid I'll do it wrong.

06:00.400 --> 06:01.240
Sure.

06:35.800 --> 06:36.880
Done.

06:39.320 --> 06:40.800
Thank you, Mr. Ji.

06:41.880 --> 06:42.840
You're welcome.

06:48.600 --> 06:49.480
Miss Yu Wei,

06:50.520 --> 06:52.360
-have we--?
-Mr. Ji,

06:53.280 --> 06:55.840
we'd better head back to the front hall.

06:56.480 --> 06:58.840
They may be questioning Master Wu.

07:00.680 --> 07:01.880
All right.

07:05.520 --> 07:07.360
I was worried about Master Wei's safety,

07:07.960 --> 07:11.280
so I secretly asked
Master Wu Shiguang to pose as the groom.

07:12.800 --> 07:14.080
Master Wu Shiguang,

07:14.920 --> 07:15.920
wait.

07:17.480 --> 07:19.160
Master Wei won't hire you,

07:19.680 --> 07:20.920
but I will.

07:24.240 --> 07:25.480
Steward Luo,

07:26.320 --> 07:27.960
my brother-in-law trusted you so much,

07:28.040 --> 07:30.520
yet you colluded with some demon hunter
of questionable background

07:30.600 --> 07:32.520
to pull something this absurd.

07:32.600 --> 07:34.280
If you really wanted help,

07:34.360 --> 07:36.840
you should've hired a real demon hunter
from the Shilin Sect.

07:37.360 --> 07:39.600
Am I right, Mr. Ji?

07:42.000 --> 07:43.160
Exactly.

07:44.880 --> 07:48.440
But Steward Luo's concern
wasn't misplaced.

07:48.520 --> 07:49.680
Master Wei was poisoned.

07:49.760 --> 07:51.320
Someone really was trying to harm him.

07:52.800 --> 07:55.040
You're suspicious of a human
instead of a demon?

07:56.320 --> 07:58.000
The fox demon is clearly
in the Wei mansion.

07:58.520 --> 07:59.840
Two people died here last night.

08:00.440 --> 08:01.680
One of them
was even a single-flower hunter

08:01.760 --> 08:03.240
from the Shilin Sect.

08:03.880 --> 08:05.080
The culprit was brutal.

08:05.160 --> 08:07.560
If I hadn't hidden
Master Wei away in advance,

08:08.080 --> 08:09.280
then maybe…

08:12.560 --> 08:13.880
I can still drink.

08:14.400 --> 08:16.600
I can still drink. Where's the wine?

08:17.600 --> 08:18.520
Wine…

08:19.320 --> 08:20.520
Let's sit down.

08:20.600 --> 08:22.600
Prepare a bowl of hangover soup
for Young Master Liu.

08:22.680 --> 08:23.680
Yes, madam.

08:26.640 --> 08:28.320
Why would a demon need poison to kill?

08:28.400 --> 08:29.800
It could just rip out hearts.

08:32.880 --> 08:34.159
The fake groom has spoken.

08:36.039 --> 08:39.120
Shouldn't the fake bride
explain herself too?

08:40.559 --> 08:43.240
Stop calling me the fake bride.

08:43.760 --> 08:45.240
I have a name.

08:45.880 --> 08:49.640
My surname, Wu, means "mist".

08:50.520 --> 08:52.360
My given name, Wangyan,
means "reckless speech".

08:53.520 --> 08:55.680
My parents gave me this name

08:55.760 --> 08:58.880
to remind me not to speak rashly.

08:59.680 --> 09:00.520
So,

09:01.360 --> 09:03.120
when I say I'm not a fox demon,

09:03.920 --> 09:04.760
I'm not.

09:07.400 --> 09:10.520
But you do carry a fox demon's aura.

09:10.600 --> 09:13.000
Master Ji Ling, have you
been paying attention to me?

09:13.840 --> 09:15.040
If you're so interested in me,

09:15.800 --> 09:17.080
why don't we talk in private?

09:20.520 --> 09:21.600
That won't be necessary.

09:23.040 --> 09:25.840
A man and a woman
shouldn't meet in private so casually.

09:25.920 --> 09:28.320
Whatever you have to say,
say it here in front of everyone.

09:41.000 --> 09:44.320
I've been searching
for this nine-tailed fox for years.

09:44.840 --> 09:46.680
It took a lot to get my hands
on this severed tail.

09:47.400 --> 09:49.640
Its connection to the fox demon

09:49.720 --> 09:51.520
led me all the way here
to the Wei mansion.

09:52.840 --> 09:54.880
It does carry
the aura of a nine-tailed fox.

09:55.400 --> 09:56.840
Why are you looking for that fox demon?

09:57.600 --> 09:58.720
Do you have some grudge against her?

10:00.840 --> 10:02.120
You could say that.

10:03.520 --> 10:06.640
That nine-tailed fox is named Xiaowei.

10:07.240 --> 10:09.480
When she fell into hardship,
a mortal saved her.

10:10.000 --> 10:11.280
To repay the debt,

10:11.360 --> 10:13.280
she kept killing people
and ripping out hearts

10:13.800 --> 10:15.280
to preserve her human form
and spiritual power,

10:15.360 --> 10:18.760
all so she could find her savior
in the vast sea of people

10:18.840 --> 10:20.760
and keep him safe and happy for life.

10:21.760 --> 10:23.120
Unfortunately,

10:23.920 --> 10:25.320
her wish was never fulfilled.

10:27.840 --> 10:29.480
<i>More than a millennium has passed,</i>

10:30.000 --> 10:32.160
<i>yet she's still obsessed</i>

10:32.680 --> 10:34.160
<i>with finding the one who saved her.</i>

10:35.000 --> 10:36.560
Did Master Wei

10:37.440 --> 10:38.560
save her?

10:39.520 --> 10:40.520
I think so.

10:41.280 --> 10:44.480
If that's the case, she must
want to kill her rival in love.

10:44.560 --> 10:46.600
That's why I posed as the bride

10:46.680 --> 10:48.480
and waited for her to walk into the trap.

10:49.080 --> 10:49.920
But instead,

10:50.680 --> 10:52.000
all I caught was a foolish pig.

10:58.320 --> 10:59.480
These days,

11:00.000 --> 11:01.760
demons all know
how to wear painted human skin.

11:02.360 --> 11:04.040
They no longer need to devour human hearts

11:04.120 --> 11:05.480
to maintain their human form.

11:06.720 --> 11:07.920
Then why is Xiaowei

11:08.640 --> 11:10.120
killing people?

11:11.200 --> 11:12.520
Demons are evil by nature.

11:13.240 --> 11:15.560
Do they need a reason to kill?

11:17.440 --> 11:18.920
Demons are bad,

11:19.840 --> 11:20.840
but humans

11:22.080 --> 11:23.880
aren't much better.

11:26.520 --> 11:28.840
Humans aren't born
knowing virtue and decency,

11:29.440 --> 11:33.240
and demons aren't always
bent on evil either.

11:34.640 --> 11:36.000
But either way,

11:37.120 --> 11:40.240
there has to be a reason for a killing.

11:41.440 --> 11:45.040
Maybe she was badly weakened
after losing a tail

11:45.760 --> 11:47.720
and needed to eat human hearts

11:48.520 --> 11:50.120
to maintain her human form.

11:51.600 --> 11:53.440
Since everyone here is under suspicion,

11:54.200 --> 11:55.960
until Xiaowei is caught,

11:56.560 --> 11:57.920
no one should leave the Wei mansion.

12:02.320 --> 12:03.760
That's unnecessary.

12:03.840 --> 12:06.680
Xiaowei's savior
is now lying in bed dying.

12:06.760 --> 12:08.280
She'll definitely find a way to save him.

12:08.800 --> 12:09.640
Why would she leave?

12:10.240 --> 12:11.560
That's only your guess.

12:13.600 --> 12:14.760
Are you Xiaowei?

12:19.080 --> 12:20.600
The fabric house is busy.

12:21.200 --> 12:22.840
Everything inside and out
needs my attention.

12:22.920 --> 12:24.560
I can't stay here forever.

12:24.640 --> 12:26.960
If you want to leave, you can.

12:28.240 --> 12:29.840
But you'll have to cooperate with me

12:30.440 --> 12:31.840
and accept my Blood Binding Seal.

12:32.440 --> 12:34.400
That way, even if you flee

12:35.000 --> 12:37.120
to the ends of the earth,
I'll still be able to track you.

12:39.320 --> 12:40.280
Wait.

12:40.360 --> 12:43.000
We're demon hunters from the Shilin Sect.

12:43.080 --> 12:44.000
Do we have to do that too?

12:45.560 --> 12:48.680
Demons can wear human skin,
and people can lie.

12:49.200 --> 12:52.000
How do I know if you're really
from the Shilin Sect?

12:53.800 --> 12:54.640
You scared me.

12:56.560 --> 12:58.280
Fine. The innocent has nothing to fear.

12:59.360 --> 13:00.360
We'll cooperate.

13:39.760 --> 13:40.600
A death curse?

13:45.360 --> 13:46.880
What… What did you do?

13:49.880 --> 13:52.400
Master Wu, what did you do?

13:52.920 --> 13:54.360
Why do you want us dead?

13:56.640 --> 13:57.640
I didn't do this.

14:02.440 --> 14:03.320
Xiaowei did.

14:04.360 --> 14:05.920
Xiaowei?

14:09.520 --> 14:11.920
How powerful is that fox demon?

14:12.520 --> 14:14.840
She managed to brand all of us

14:15.720 --> 14:17.480
with a death curse mark
without anyone noticing?

14:17.560 --> 14:18.440
No,

14:19.320 --> 14:20.800
that's not necessarily true.

14:21.360 --> 14:22.480
She might have set conditions

14:22.560 --> 14:24.200
so the curse
would be triggered automatically.

14:25.040 --> 14:28.120
For example, she could make it
so that if all of us did something

14:28.200 --> 14:29.400
or failed to do something
at the same time,

14:30.000 --> 14:31.360
the death curse would be triggered.

14:34.840 --> 14:35.840
I get it now!

14:39.880 --> 14:41.400
None of us brought a wedding gift.

14:42.560 --> 14:46.000
Gentlemen, to prevent confusion,
please tell us your names

14:46.080 --> 14:47.880
and leave your gifts here.

14:48.680 --> 14:50.200
You and Wu Wangyan
were posing as the groom and bride,

14:50.800 --> 14:52.040
so naturally,
you didn't prepare any gifts.

14:52.640 --> 14:53.760
Xiaowei

14:53.840 --> 14:55.880
must've linked the curse
to the gift record.

14:59.360 --> 15:02.160
GIFT RECORD

15:02.760 --> 15:04.400
Anyone who entered
the Wei mansion without a gift

15:05.000 --> 15:07.080
must have ulterior motives.

15:07.160 --> 15:10.160
Using that condition to filter people out

15:10.240 --> 15:11.120
truly is a clever move.

15:14.520 --> 15:15.680
Miss Yu Wei,

15:15.760 --> 15:17.920
how come you didn't bring a gift either?

15:23.960 --> 15:26.200
I don't have the money.

15:29.000 --> 15:30.080
I'm sorry.

15:30.160 --> 15:31.520
It's fine.

15:34.120 --> 15:35.440
What now?

15:40.760 --> 15:42.560
The mark looks like a moon phase.

15:43.160 --> 15:44.920
And it's slowly shifting.

15:45.520 --> 15:47.040
Just now, it was full.

15:47.840 --> 15:49.560
Now it's already a waning crescent.

15:54.080 --> 15:55.520
A death curse eats away

15:56.040 --> 15:57.440
at one's lifespan day by day.

15:58.880 --> 16:00.560
Once it's fully consumed,
one will be dead.

16:01.880 --> 16:02.920
I don't want to die.

16:03.520 --> 16:05.720
We may have been cursed,
but we've gained something too.

16:06.440 --> 16:08.240
The suspect pool just got a lot smaller,

16:08.920 --> 16:09.800
didn't it?

16:11.520 --> 16:14.680
I assume the three of you don't have
the curse mark on your hands, right?

16:21.080 --> 16:21.920
Pig.

16:24.680 --> 16:25.720
You…

17:00.080 --> 17:02.000
Of the three people
without the curse mark,

17:02.080 --> 17:03.360
Liu Weixue is the one I suspect most.

17:03.880 --> 17:06.200
He was so drunk, he could barely
tell east from west,

17:06.280 --> 17:09.079
yet somehow he happened
to stagger into the weaving workshop?

17:09.599 --> 17:10.440
I don't buy it.

17:10.520 --> 17:12.160
Good. You shouldn't.

17:13.240 --> 17:14.960
He went there specifically
to find Luo Wei.

17:16.839 --> 17:18.000
Luo Wei?

17:33.400 --> 17:34.600
What's that?

17:35.800 --> 17:37.920
Master Wu Shiguang set up a barrier.

17:39.960 --> 17:42.400
He said it could stop demons
from hurting people.

17:45.120 --> 17:47.200
Good. Good.

17:48.240 --> 17:50.440
Have some tea and sober up.

17:51.160 --> 17:52.120
Young Master Liu,

17:52.720 --> 17:54.560
please don't drink so much again.

17:55.080 --> 17:56.360
It's too hard on your body.

17:58.120 --> 18:00.960
I only drank that much
because I was shielding you from the wine.

18:01.880 --> 18:02.920
Luo Wei…

18:13.000 --> 18:15.200
What do I have to do

18:17.000 --> 18:18.800
for you to finally care about me?

18:20.520 --> 18:21.680
Young Master Liu,

18:22.800 --> 18:24.280
fate is predetermined.

18:25.840 --> 18:27.040
It can't be forced.

18:28.400 --> 18:31.840
Everyone says Weimiao Pavilion
is the best place to pray for love.

18:31.920 --> 18:33.720
If I went to ask for a talisman,

18:34.240 --> 18:35.560
would your heart…

18:36.480 --> 18:39.000
Would your heart finally be mine?

18:42.440 --> 18:43.920
But anyone can see

18:44.000 --> 18:46.160
Wei Qing is the only one Luo Wei loves.

18:47.560 --> 18:49.720
The Wei mansion may not be big,

18:49.800 --> 18:51.680
but the relationships here
are all tangled up.

18:53.080 --> 18:54.360
What a headache.

18:55.640 --> 18:57.520
He was obviously drunk.

18:59.400 --> 19:00.720
How could he have killed anyone?

19:00.800 --> 19:02.520
Ms. Yu said

19:03.400 --> 19:04.560
that last night, Steward Luo took her

19:04.640 --> 19:06.720
to the weaving workshop
right after she entered the Wei mansion.

19:07.320 --> 19:08.840
She and Steward Luo
can vouch for each other.

19:23.520 --> 19:24.880
Vouching for each other

19:25.480 --> 19:27.360
can also mean covering for each other.

19:37.600 --> 19:38.600
What a headache.

19:39.440 --> 19:42.520
Why does everyone seem innocent
and suspicious at the same time?

19:43.160 --> 19:44.160
It's driving me crazy.

19:44.240 --> 19:45.680
Who is Xiaowei, really?

19:46.400 --> 19:50.760
Don't worry. A fox will show
its tail sooner or later.

19:52.640 --> 19:53.640
What's wrong?

19:59.240 --> 20:00.360
I've lost my sense of touch.

20:01.280 --> 20:02.360
What do we do now?

20:02.880 --> 20:05.520
-I don't want to be the one to bury you.
-Shut up.

20:05.600 --> 20:07.280
If I were Xiaowei,

20:07.880 --> 20:10.000
I'd put the death curse on myself too.

20:10.920 --> 20:12.880
But when that scream rang out…

20:15.920 --> 20:17.760
Wu Wangyan, Ji Ling, Li Jie,

20:17.840 --> 20:20.120
and Yu Wei were all with you.

20:21.000 --> 20:22.640
Who would've had time to rip out a heart?

20:22.720 --> 20:24.040
There are countless demonic arts.

20:24.560 --> 20:26.440
A demon can kill from 1,000 li away.

20:27.320 --> 20:29.800
Besides, what if Xiaowei
wasn't working alone?

20:29.880 --> 20:31.720
Couldn't she have had an accomplice?

20:32.680 --> 20:33.520
Good point.

20:33.600 --> 20:36.880
Even I've got a capable
right-hand man like you.

20:38.920 --> 20:40.200
Who do you suspect most?

20:42.360 --> 20:43.520
Wu Wangyan.

20:46.240 --> 20:47.400
And Yu Wei.

20:53.360 --> 20:54.240
Wangyan.

20:55.160 --> 20:57.040
What are you doing?

20:58.640 --> 21:00.520
The death curse
is starting to take effect.

21:01.040 --> 21:02.640
I've lost my sense of touch.

21:03.240 --> 21:04.360
It doesn't hurt.

21:07.200 --> 21:08.480
Don't worry.

21:09.600 --> 21:11.680
Right, and there's Ji Ling too.

21:11.760 --> 21:14.480
He's just an ordinary demon hunter
with no sacred power,

21:15.240 --> 21:16.520
yet that Shilin Sect commander

21:16.600 --> 21:18.280
obeys him without question
and never leaves his side.

21:18.920 --> 21:20.120
Something's definitely off.

21:23.400 --> 21:25.360
I can't even taste
these roasted ginkgo nuts anymore.

21:26.120 --> 21:27.200
This is awful.

21:27.280 --> 21:29.960
The death curse
will gradually strip away our senses

21:30.040 --> 21:31.880
until all five are gone.

21:31.960 --> 21:34.000
The day this mark turns completely dark

21:34.680 --> 21:36.640
will be the day we die.

21:37.760 --> 21:39.120
Xiaowei truly is vile.

21:40.480 --> 21:43.600
We've got to find a way
to make her slip up and show herself.

21:45.680 --> 21:47.920
The Shilin Sect's demon hunters
obey their commander.

21:48.520 --> 21:51.160
Who does the commander answer to?

21:51.240 --> 21:52.360
The Dragon Deity.

21:56.440 --> 21:57.440
The Dragon Deity?

21:59.080 --> 22:00.120
No way.

22:00.720 --> 22:03.040
That silly boy is the Dragon Deity?

22:03.120 --> 22:05.440
But how could the Dragon Deity
have no sacred power?

22:05.960 --> 22:06.800
There's always been a rumor

22:06.880 --> 22:09.800
that Chi Wen was badly wounded
in that great calamity

22:10.400 --> 22:12.200
and lost all of his Dragon Deity's Power.

22:14.880 --> 22:17.240
Do you remember the ring
on Ji Ling's hand?

22:18.400 --> 22:22.960
He was able to use demon magic
only with the help of that ring.

22:23.040 --> 22:25.000
We traced the demonic energy right here.

22:25.080 --> 22:26.840
You're the nine-tailed fox
who ripped out hearts!

22:28.240 --> 22:29.680
Then isn't this just what we wanted?

22:30.440 --> 22:31.640
Now we can kill the Dragon Deity

22:33.280 --> 22:34.720
without going to the Shilin Sect.

22:36.040 --> 22:37.400
I don't think it's that simple.

22:38.000 --> 22:39.320
Let's wait a bit longer.

22:41.280 --> 22:42.640
We need to survive first.

22:46.920 --> 22:48.520
Now, I need to visit somewhere first.

22:50.480 --> 22:51.640
Weimiao Pavilion?

22:52.520 --> 22:53.560
Wangyan,

22:54.800 --> 22:56.400
what's your plan?

22:57.840 --> 22:59.600
Are we really just going to sit here

23:01.520 --> 23:02.960
and wait for the death curse

23:04.760 --> 23:06.280
to take our lives?

23:06.800 --> 23:10.480
Catch Xiaowei,
and the death curse will be lifted.

23:11.600 --> 23:14.960
Besides, Ji Ling and Wu Shiguang
are cursed too.

23:16.000 --> 23:18.240
They won't sit around waiting to die.

23:19.280 --> 23:22.360
They're even more anxious than we are.

23:24.560 --> 23:26.240
Are they really that powerful?

23:27.080 --> 23:28.520
Let's not even get into the rest.

23:29.040 --> 23:32.040
Wu Shiguang's prayer bead bracelet alone
is no ordinary artifact.

23:32.120 --> 23:34.240
It's called the Twelve Thoughts.

23:34.320 --> 23:38.040
The beads were forged
from the blood of 12 vicious sinners

23:38.120 --> 23:40.960
and embodied 12 different thoughts.

23:41.040 --> 23:44.960
Benevolence, malice, greed,

23:45.720 --> 23:48.160
obsession, desire,

23:48.920 --> 23:49.800
delusion…

23:50.320 --> 23:51.920
All right, enough.

23:53.160 --> 23:55.480
If that artifact is really so powerful,

23:56.320 --> 23:58.920
how did it end up in the hands
of some wandering demon hunter?

24:01.120 --> 24:04.320
Do you really think he's just
some ordinary wandering demon hunter?

24:07.440 --> 24:08.320
What about Ji Ling?

24:12.120 --> 24:13.200
What do you think?

24:18.880 --> 24:21.160
He's clearly a simple-minded fool.

24:21.240 --> 24:24.120
Smile at him,
and he'd hand over his life to you.

24:28.360 --> 24:29.440
Wrong.

24:30.160 --> 24:32.520
He's even more mysterious
than Wu Shiguang.

24:33.480 --> 24:34.760
Don't let your guard down.

24:36.840 --> 24:37.960
Interesting.

24:40.360 --> 24:43.280
Then I'll go spend some time
with this man fate chose for me.

24:57.560 --> 24:58.400
You scared me.

24:59.200 --> 25:00.360
I found nothing.

25:50.400 --> 25:51.400
Actually, I…

25:59.560 --> 26:00.840
Miss Yu Wei,

26:01.400 --> 26:03.200
you hit me way too hard.

26:04.120 --> 26:06.640
Why did you hide in there? You scared me.

26:07.160 --> 26:11.200
I thought you were some creep.

26:11.280 --> 26:13.080
You clearly saw it was me.

26:14.000 --> 26:15.480
You did that on purpose, didn't you?

26:16.440 --> 26:19.720
It was so dark in there.

26:19.800 --> 26:22.640
I couldn't see clearly at all.

26:25.000 --> 26:25.840
Well,

26:26.840 --> 26:28.160
can you see clearly now?

26:30.200 --> 26:32.120
I should have the kind of face

26:32.680 --> 26:34.400
people never forget, right?

26:36.280 --> 26:37.480
Very handsome.

26:38.160 --> 26:40.800
So tell me,

26:42.040 --> 26:44.880
do you think I'm handsome?

26:46.680 --> 26:48.320
Or do I look familiar to you?

26:49.680 --> 26:50.960
Not at all.

26:51.920 --> 26:52.760
I don't look familiar?

26:53.360 --> 26:54.240
She means not handsome.

26:57.080 --> 26:57.880
Thanks.

27:02.280 --> 27:04.600
Why are you in Luo Wei's room?

27:05.520 --> 27:06.840
And why were you hiding in the cabinet?

27:07.960 --> 27:09.800
We're here to investigate. What about you?

27:09.880 --> 27:11.320
I'm here to investigate too.

27:13.560 --> 27:15.960
You… You're here to hunt the demon too?

27:16.040 --> 27:17.280
Are you a demon hunter?

27:17.880 --> 27:19.080
Are you a demon hunter?

27:21.760 --> 27:23.560
I'm just an ordinary person.

27:23.640 --> 27:25.080
How could I be a demon hunter?

27:25.160 --> 27:28.400
I'm only investigating
to save my own life.

27:28.480 --> 27:30.280
If we don't find Xiaowei soon,

27:32.800 --> 27:36.160
how are we supposed
to break this death curse?

27:39.720 --> 27:42.360
I found Steward Luo very suspicious,

27:42.880 --> 27:44.120
so I thought I'd start with her.

27:49.600 --> 27:51.680
Everyone, we're here.

27:51.760 --> 27:53.080
Watch your step.

27:54.200 --> 27:55.760
-We're here.
-Watch your step.

27:55.840 --> 27:56.960
This is the place.

27:59.560 --> 28:00.880
Rouge for sale!

28:09.880 --> 28:11.080
This way.

28:14.160 --> 28:15.800
-Let's hang ours over here.
-Finest rouge!

28:15.880 --> 28:16.800
Come and have a look.

28:30.200 --> 28:31.040
Over here! Come.

28:32.360 --> 28:33.600
The Energy-Draining Spell?

28:34.600 --> 28:36.000
<i>Tanghulu</i>!

28:36.520 --> 28:38.480
WEIMIAO PAVILION

28:41.640 --> 28:43.440
Looks like someone's hiding inside,

28:44.760 --> 28:46.920
cultivating demon magic by absorbing

28:48.000 --> 28:49.440
mortals' heart energy.

28:51.520 --> 28:52.640
<i>Someone?</i>

28:52.720 --> 28:53.920
<i>You mean a demon.</i>

28:54.000 --> 28:55.160
<i>Be careful.</i>

28:57.320 --> 28:58.680
Yes, Lady Wei.

28:58.760 --> 29:00.760
Understood. I'll handle it now.

29:09.160 --> 29:10.000
Miss,

29:11.240 --> 29:13.120
what do people pray for
at Weimiao Pavilion?

29:13.760 --> 29:15.600
This is a pavilion of love.

29:15.680 --> 29:17.120
People come here to pray
for romance, of course.

29:19.360 --> 29:21.920
So that's where
all that heart energy comes from.

29:22.000 --> 29:23.800
No wonder I see pink everywhere.

29:24.400 --> 29:25.400
He's so handsome.

29:25.480 --> 29:27.560
It can't be happening this fast, can it?

29:27.640 --> 29:29.600
This place really works.

29:30.200 --> 29:32.280
Darling, why did you walk so fast?

29:32.880 --> 29:34.440
You should've waited for me.

29:40.200 --> 29:41.240
Miss,

29:41.320 --> 29:44.440
I've heard that praying for love
at Weimiao Pavilion really works.

29:44.520 --> 29:45.360
Is that true?

29:46.600 --> 29:48.040
I used to think so too.

29:48.880 --> 29:50.240
Now?

29:50.840 --> 29:52.000
I'd say it's just so-so.

29:52.720 --> 29:55.280
But they all say
the love talismans here work wonders.

29:56.200 --> 30:00.880
You two don't really look
like you need Lady Wei's love talisman.

30:01.600 --> 30:03.560
-We…
-Lady Wei?

30:04.120 --> 30:07.120
Anyway, if you really want one…

30:34.840 --> 30:35.880
What did she tell you?

30:36.800 --> 30:37.840
Curious?

30:39.120 --> 30:39.960
I am.

30:40.040 --> 30:41.480
Beg, and I'll tell.

30:48.320 --> 30:52.040
She said that
if you wanted a love talisman,

30:52.120 --> 30:53.840
you'd have to take off all your clothes

30:53.920 --> 30:55.600
and bare yourself completely.

30:57.040 --> 30:58.840
I wasn't finished.

30:59.520 --> 31:03.160
After you take off your clothes,
you need to tell Lady Wei a secret.

31:03.240 --> 31:04.520
You're making this up.

31:04.600 --> 31:06.600
Remember? I don't lie.

31:07.240 --> 31:09.160
You have to undress to go inside
and ask for a talisman?

31:11.800 --> 31:14.320
Also, why are you following me?

31:19.880 --> 31:22.200
<i>Tanghulu</i>!

31:23.040 --> 31:25.360
<i>Tanghulu</i>!

31:25.440 --> 31:28.240
Scented sachets and pendants!

31:33.400 --> 31:36.200
I wasn't following you.

31:39.960 --> 31:41.280
You're suspicious of her?

31:43.800 --> 31:46.120
But last night,
she was with Ms. Yu all night.

31:49.160 --> 31:51.040
I wasn't exactly with her all night.

31:51.560 --> 31:53.440
There are too many guests.

31:53.520 --> 31:54.520
We can't let them find out

31:54.600 --> 31:56.240
the bride never went through
with the ceremony.

31:56.320 --> 31:57.280
I'll take you to the weaving workshop.

31:57.360 --> 31:58.920
Hide there for now.

32:03.240 --> 32:07.120
After Steward Luo took me
to the weaving workshop, she left.

32:07.760 --> 32:10.680
I asked her to bring Wei Qing to me.

32:12.640 --> 32:14.800
I was worried about Master Wei's safety,

32:14.880 --> 32:18.200
so I secretly asked
Master Wu Shiguang to pose as the groom.

32:18.280 --> 32:20.320
But she knew

32:20.920 --> 32:23.520
Wei Qing was locked
inside a cabinet in the workshop.

32:24.240 --> 32:25.360
Exactly.

32:25.440 --> 32:27.440
Such a blatant contradiction.

32:27.520 --> 32:31.320
Now, don't you think
she's highly suspicious?

32:31.960 --> 32:34.960
Luo Wei's only been at the Wei mansion
for a little over a month.

32:35.040 --> 32:38.120
No one in the household
knows where she came from.

32:38.200 --> 32:39.280
She's the only outsider living here.

32:40.000 --> 32:42.320
Don't you think she's highly suspicious?

32:43.560 --> 32:45.600
We've already looked into Luo Wei.

32:52.000 --> 32:53.280
Luo Wei,

32:53.360 --> 32:56.360
born in the old town, is an orphan

32:57.240 --> 32:59.360
and was raised by a rural healer.

32:59.880 --> 33:02.840
It is said that the healer
knew a thing or two about poison.

33:03.480 --> 33:06.480
We suspected she poisoned Wei Qing,

33:06.560 --> 33:08.000
so we came to her room
to look for evidence.

33:09.040 --> 33:10.480
I knew something was off about her.

33:12.520 --> 33:14.480
Thank goodness we have you, Mr. Ji.

33:15.000 --> 33:16.160
Otherwise,

33:17.040 --> 33:19.120
the whole Wei family
would've been destroyed.

33:20.720 --> 33:23.560
You're not a demon hunter,
so don't worry about it.

33:24.080 --> 33:25.520
That fox demon is dangerous.

33:25.600 --> 33:27.120
Leave it to the Shilin Sect
to deal with her.

33:29.560 --> 33:32.440
That other Shilin Sect hunter
was too weak.

33:33.880 --> 33:36.240
Mr. Ji, if you'd come a little sooner,

33:36.320 --> 33:38.440
I would've had someone to rely on.

33:41.200 --> 33:42.080
Ji,

33:43.040 --> 33:44.000
thank you.

33:49.200 --> 33:51.520
"Ji"?

33:53.640 --> 33:54.720
I'm just worried about my cousin.

33:57.560 --> 33:59.280
You mean Ms. Yu Shengwei?

33:59.800 --> 34:01.520
You two are so close.

34:02.720 --> 34:03.680
At a time like this,

34:04.280 --> 34:06.400
how can Luo Wei still be in the mood
to pray for love?

34:07.200 --> 34:09.159
Is she really in love with Wei Qing?

34:10.080 --> 34:12.679
Shiguang, I'm afraid you've never seen

34:12.760 --> 34:16.199
what a woman
who's truly in love looks like.

34:16.280 --> 34:17.360
My surname is Wu.

34:17.880 --> 34:19.000
You can call me Master Wu.

34:19.800 --> 34:20.840
Love

34:20.920 --> 34:23.760
can make someone holding
a sharp blade cast aside their weapon.

34:23.840 --> 34:26.080
It can make the proud
and arrogant lower their heads.

34:26.760 --> 34:28.920
It can make someone clad in armor
show their weakness.

34:29.639 --> 34:31.080
It can make the cleverest person

34:31.159 --> 34:33.600
do the stupidest things in the world.

34:34.400 --> 34:36.159
It can even make one forget
where they came from

34:36.239 --> 34:37.560
and where they're going.

34:40.440 --> 34:41.520
I came by boat,

34:42.040 --> 34:43.480
and I plan to walk back later.

34:45.000 --> 34:46.960
Look. What is this?

34:48.480 --> 34:49.600
Wood.

34:51.120 --> 34:52.960
That's what you're made of.

34:55.159 --> 34:58.400
You make mutual love
between a man and a woman

34:58.920 --> 35:00.320
sound like some kind of sorcery.

35:00.920 --> 35:03.760
Love is sorcery.

35:04.320 --> 35:06.920
No, it's even
more terrifying than sorcery.

35:07.440 --> 35:09.440
Tell me, does Luo Wei strike you

35:09.520 --> 35:12.560
as someone who would
do crazy things for love?

35:15.640 --> 35:17.320
Compared with ordinary women,

35:17.400 --> 35:20.000
she's far more meticulous,
and she hides her sharpness deep within.

35:20.920 --> 35:21.800
So, no, she doesn't.

35:21.880 --> 35:23.440
Shiguang, you're so clever.

35:24.040 --> 35:26.360
-Wangyan, your name suits you well.
-Thanks.

35:43.680 --> 35:44.640
Found it.

35:47.360 --> 35:48.560
Mr. Ji,

35:49.280 --> 35:51.000
if you don't let go of my hand,

35:51.520 --> 35:52.760
how am I supposed to give it to you?

36:05.120 --> 36:06.280
Here.

36:12.960 --> 36:13.800
It's the antidote.

36:15.600 --> 36:17.040
You can tell just by smelling it?

36:17.120 --> 36:19.920
I am a pharmacology genius
who's read widely.

36:20.520 --> 36:21.520
The evidence is conclusive now.

36:23.120 --> 36:26.040
Looks like beautiful women are all liars.

36:28.800 --> 36:30.560
Why are you insulting yourself?

36:34.120 --> 36:35.720
So you think I'm pretty, Ji?

36:38.920 --> 36:41.360
I think we've all underestimated Luo Wei.

36:41.960 --> 36:45.960
Jealousy born of unrequited love
is only her disguise.

36:46.040 --> 36:49.040
What she really wants isn't Wei Qing.

36:49.800 --> 36:50.960
It's this entire Wei mansion.

36:55.440 --> 36:56.440
Miss Yu Wei.

37:06.800 --> 37:07.800
Come on. Let's go.

37:07.880 --> 37:09.000
Why are you still standing there?

37:09.640 --> 37:10.800
"Zhao Xiao'e."

37:10.880 --> 37:12.080
What?

37:16.920 --> 37:18.680
A victim's wife

37:18.760 --> 37:21.720
is named Zhao Xiao'e.

37:22.240 --> 37:24.960
ZHAO XIAO'E

37:25.040 --> 37:25.880
<i>Wake up!</i>

37:35.320 --> 37:37.280
Li Mao, the man who died
at the Wei mansion last night,

37:38.040 --> 37:39.680
was holding this talisman too.

37:41.400 --> 37:44.480
I also came here because of this talisman.

37:45.800 --> 37:49.040
Could it be that all the victims' partners

37:49.680 --> 37:51.480
once came to Weimiao Pavilion?

37:55.600 --> 37:56.920
We'll know once we look.

38:00.560 --> 38:01.600
"Chen Geng"?

38:15.360 --> 38:16.360
"Sun Zhiniang."

38:30.360 --> 38:31.240
Li Mao's wife,

38:31.920 --> 38:33.080
Tao Xi.

38:45.520 --> 38:46.360
It seems

38:47.520 --> 38:48.760
we really do need to go inside.

38:50.360 --> 38:54.000
WEIMIAO PAVILION

39:16.320 --> 39:17.160
He's awake.

39:22.600 --> 39:23.480
Easy now.

39:23.560 --> 39:24.760
What happened to me?

39:24.840 --> 39:27.800
You were poisoned, but you're fine now.

39:28.920 --> 39:30.040
Poisoned?

39:32.000 --> 39:33.040
Why don't I remember anything?

39:33.680 --> 39:35.800
Luo Wei poisoned you.

39:36.640 --> 39:37.600
Luo Wei?

39:40.800 --> 39:42.520
Why would she do that?

39:44.680 --> 39:46.640
Where is she? I need to find her.

39:47.440 --> 39:49.600
You… You should rest first.

40:09.600 --> 40:11.920
A couple coming here together
to pray for love? That's new.

40:12.000 --> 40:13.320
How interesting.

40:14.440 --> 40:15.960
-We're not--
-What can we do?

40:16.040 --> 40:17.240
We just love each other too much.

40:17.840 --> 40:19.040
We're here to pray

40:19.120 --> 40:20.600
that we'll still be a couple
in the next life.

40:21.200 --> 40:22.440
Isn't that right, darling?

40:22.520 --> 40:24.080
Lady Wei is out traveling.

40:24.160 --> 40:25.600
She won't be here for quite a while.

40:25.680 --> 40:27.160
Please come back another time.

40:27.240 --> 40:29.120
But someone just came out with a talisman.

40:34.240 --> 40:36.400
Lady Wei isn't here,

40:36.480 --> 40:38.240
but if you follow the rules,

40:38.320 --> 40:40.000
the love talisman may still be granted.

40:42.880 --> 40:43.720
I don't have any money.

40:51.440 --> 40:52.280
Really, I don't.

41:04.800 --> 41:05.760
Besides a donation,

41:05.840 --> 41:08.440
you also have to write down a secret
and put it in the box.

41:10.600 --> 41:11.440
A secret?

41:12.400 --> 41:13.360
Why?

41:13.440 --> 41:15.360
Lady Wei likes secrets.

41:15.440 --> 41:17.600
She thinks they are
the most powerful force in the world.

41:18.200 --> 41:22.240
Besides, isn't mortals' unrequited love
a kind of secret too?

41:25.000 --> 41:26.000
Fair point.

41:59.120 --> 42:01.200
My… copper coin.

42:01.280 --> 42:02.800
Looks like what you wrote was a lie.

42:03.440 --> 42:06.480
Without sincerity, you'll never
get a talisman that works.

42:06.560 --> 42:07.800
Leave now.

42:07.880 --> 42:09.040
Stop wasting your time.

42:11.400 --> 42:12.600
I told you so.

42:13.120 --> 42:14.600
We shouldn't have bothered.

42:40.320 --> 42:41.800
Hiding private savings, are you?

42:44.720 --> 42:46.360
If you don't want to die,

42:47.040 --> 42:49.480
answer my questions.

42:50.680 --> 42:54.440
Any connection between the heart-ripping
murders and the love talismans

42:54.520 --> 42:56.480
you handed out?

42:57.160 --> 42:58.560
This concerns Lady Wei.

42:59.200 --> 43:01.880
Even if you kill me, I won't say a word.

43:07.560 --> 43:08.560
Let me.

43:11.760 --> 43:12.960
Tell me.

43:13.520 --> 43:14.720
Are the heart-ripping murders in the city

43:14.800 --> 43:17.040
connected to the love talismans

43:17.120 --> 43:18.920
you handed out?

43:19.960 --> 43:22.880
The love talismans
carry a Fox-Allure Spell.

43:22.960 --> 43:24.920
They can make the one
who asks for the talisman

43:25.000 --> 43:27.200
win the affection of the one they love

43:27.280 --> 43:28.960
and become their partner.

43:29.960 --> 43:31.480
Is there a price to pay?

43:32.080 --> 43:34.800
If the one who asked
for the talisman falls for someone else

43:34.880 --> 43:36.480
and regrets the union,

43:36.560 --> 43:38.600
they can tear up the talisman,

43:38.680 --> 43:41.120
but their partner
will suffer the consequences.

43:41.720 --> 43:43.560
They'll be racked with heartache.

43:43.640 --> 43:46.160
Eventually, they'll rip out
their own heart and die.

43:55.040 --> 43:56.800
When the one who asked
for the talisman falls for someone else,

43:57.320 --> 43:59.000
their partner will die.

44:00.240 --> 44:02.320
What a vicious spell.
